{"tid":1716094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］ 今晚一定要休息","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:47:28.000Z","uid":243941,"like":10,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"89a72cea60c55aa9f3dc54082bd8224dffd33d28","tid":1716094,"uid":243941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"各大商場 16:00 關閉<br />\n港交所 提早收工<br />\n馬會取消賽事<br />\n港島區醫院收到通知要做好準備<br />\n中大接走NDS<br />\n<br />\n對於工作咗一日嘅市民，綜合以上原因，好好返屋企休息一晚，唔好出街shopping，聽日繼續！<br />\n<br />\n而同學仔就唔好咁好學，清潔好校園就快d離開！<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b128ba2bd37c04dbcc69786becc310158b85aa3","tid":1716094,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"早睡早起"},{"pid":"a51d0d5cb89a8a597e514b3bff0620378b914ca8","tid":1716094,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"1206ff62c0f35e820b5f997acba633b61d615a6e","tid":1716094,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2cac32dfcd4eec12398ee530182c1efdccd27b","tid":1716094,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"聽日再塞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f78b45899c266ee38fb2c07b73aa56cfcc0075","tid":1716094,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a72cea60c55aa9f3dc54082bd8224dffd33d28","tid":1716094,"uid":243941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"各大商場 16:00 關閉<br />\n港交所 提早收工<br />\n馬會取消賽事<br />\n港島區醫院收到通知要做好準備<br />\n中大接走NDS<br />\n<br />\n對於工作咗一日嘅市民，綜合以上原因，好好返屋企休息一晚，唔好出街shopping，聽日繼續！<br />\n<br />\n而同學仔就唔好咁好學，清潔好校園就快d離開！<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"ec65ed6cef0dd1152ad2c244e5e5ff53752fe5ba","tid":1716094,"uid":92230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"強攻不下就吹風撤退<br />\n收皮啦休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c08a1c5749b02f6ab847870af7a417f499e50e","tid":1716094,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"08e9a6654225276b0e186374ce65a0bd3c2c5517","tid":1716094,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"休你老母<br />\n中